title: 124: Our Family Vacation Mishaps | Ear Biscuits Ep. 124
description:
Rhett & Link sit down to talk their recent family vacations to Hawaii & Mexico, why they chose not to vacation together this year, and some of the misadventures they found themselves on while traveling with their families on this week's Ear Biscuits.
